  <div id="text-content_e7ce989e-adb9-4a4d-9576-7d7a5bebb6bc" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you have <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-allow-students-to-like-replies-in-a-discussion/ta-p/1027" target="_blank">allowed liking for a course discussion</a>, you can like discussion replies.</p>
<p>If the steps in this lesson do not match what is displayed in your course, learn how to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-like-a-reply-in-a-course-discussion-as-an-instructor/ta-p/1288" target="_blank">like discussion replies in the classic Discussions interface</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussions" data-step-uuid="3a095006-64a0-4730-92fe-d8d566ce9b85">
    <h2 id="open_discussions" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussions</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/447/416/original/ecb79d5f-3e08-44f5-a11a-a54f7710b487.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussions" height="258" width="175">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_210b4444-66fa-46b3-8f6f-853a1a8a0a6d" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Discussions</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussion" data-step-uuid="7a5ad79c-1ec2-4be8-ad67-5541a3c176e2">
    <h2 id="open_discussion" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussion</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/447/418/original/79dde0df-9162-4501-b22b-6603c4545bcc.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussion" height="287" width="799">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_5ed9bba5-d06f-4e94-adec-3c2569701aa1" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the name of the discussion.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="like_discussion_reply" data-step-uuid="a1c335e1-f182-47ac-bbba-90d0d249a7bc">
    <h2 id="like_discussion_reply" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Like Discussion Reply</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/733/285/original/cecaddbe-c817-40a2-a7e2-701e25bf5762.png" srcset="" alt="Like Discussion Reply" height="313" width="699">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_0700c288-bfd2-4781-8f37-dba466a6f4cf" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate the reply and click the <strong>Like </strong>icon.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view_liked_discussion" data-step-uuid="42c66855-0986-4759-b599-7b5c08d3966d">
    <h3 id="view_liked_discussion" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Liked Discussion</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/733/288/original/1f2c93fd-62cb-468c-93b3-3d0fc454a6bf.png" srcset="" alt="View Liked Discussion" height="274" width="699">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_37d562b3-ef67-42db-a36c-4e1bfc043cbe" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The Like icon will fill in, indicating you have liked the reply [1].</p>
<p>The Like icon also displays the total number of times a reply has been liked [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
